# ── Contact form ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Free access key from https://web3forms.com — create it against your REAL
# inbox (e.g. contact@ardmupro.ch). That address is stored on Web3Forms and
# is NEVER exposed to visitors; only this key lives in the app.
# Set this in your hosting provider's env (e.g. Vercel → Project → Settings →
# Environment Variables) and redeploy. Without it the form falls back to
# opening the visitor's mail client to the public address.
WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
